CHANGELOG

0.0.1 - Initial Creation
	  - Lots of things "hardcoded"
	  - No response to some http headers
	  - Could serve only html
0.0.6 - Implemented HTTP HEAD request
      - Unhardcoded things like version numbers and updated
      - Changed mime-type handler - still need a better version I think
      - Added in a 501 response for a HTTP POST request
0.1.0 - Started working on using inifile gem
	  - Added in logging via logger gem


